```plantuml
@startuml miztiik_aws-real-time-use-cases

actor User

participant "AWS Use Case Catalog" as Catalog
participant "Metadata System" as Metadata
participant "External Resources" as External
participant "Community Contribution System" as Contribution

User -> Catalog: Browse Use Cases
Catalog -> User: Display Use Cases
User -> Catalog: Select a Use Case
Catalog -> Metadata: Retrieve Metadata
Metadata -> Catalog: Return Metadata
Catalog -> External: Fetch Additional Resources
External -> Catalog: Return Resources
Catalog -> User: Display Use Case Details

User -> Contribution: Submit New Use Case
Contribution -> Catalog: Validate Submission
Catalog -> Contribution: Confirm Submission

@enduml
```